      <p><a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">Dromites</a> stand about 3 feet tall and usually weigh slightly more than 30 pounds. They have iridescent compound eyes. <a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">Dromites</a> wear heavy boots and light clothing, and are sometimes content with just a sturdy harness.</p>
      <p><a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">Dromites</a> speak Common.</p>
      <p>Most <a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">dromites</a> encountered outside their homes are warriors; the information in the statistics block is for a warrior of 1st level.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
