          <a class="indexterm" name="PsionicMonsters119"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Psi-Like Abilities:</strong></span> 1/day: <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch57.html#PsionicPowersD-F93">energy ray</a></em></span> (fire, 1d6+1)<span class="emphasis"><em/></span>. Manifester level 1st. The save DC is Charisma-based. (Other <a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">dromites</a> may manifest electricity, cold, or sonic <span class="emphasis"><em>energy rays</em></span> instead; the <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch57.html#PsionicPowersD-F93">energy ray</a></em></span> always matches the type of energy the <a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">dromite</a> is resistant to.)</p>
          <p>The <a href="ch77s10.html#PsionicMonsters117">dromite</a> warrior presented here had the following ability scores before racial adjustments: Str 13, Dex 11, Con 12, Int 10, Wis 9, Cha 8.</p>
        </div>
